2007-09-07  Marcus Brinkmann  <marcus@g10code.de>

	* assuan-inquire.c (assuan_inquire_ext): If MAXLEN is 0, still
	initialize MEMBUF.

	* assuan-inquire.c (_assuan_inquire_ext_cb): Clear CTX->in_inquire
	before invoking callback and returning.

