	LOGERRORX):  Remove.
	(LOG): New macro.
	(domain_reader): Use it.
	(domain_writer): Likewise.
	(domain_sendfd): Likewise.
	(domain_receivefd): Likewise.
	(_assuan_domain_init): Likewise.
	(assuan_domain_connect): Likewise.
